  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "There are 13 seats in the opposition, including GL and Dallas",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Professor G.L. who is the chairman of Sri Lanka Podujana Peramuna. Thirteen members of that party, including Mr. Peiris, became independent from the government and took seats in the opposition.",
        "G.L. In addition to Mr. Peiris, Dallas Alahapperuma, lawyer Dylan Perera, Dr. Nalaka Godaheva, Professor Charita Herath, Professor Channa Jayasumana, S. Kumarasiri, Dr. Gunapala Ratnasekara, Advocate Udayana Kirindigoda, Advocate Wasantha Yapa Bandara, Dr. Upul Galappatti, Dr. Tilak Rajapaksa, and Lalith Ellawala went to the opposition and sat down.",
        "Professor G.L. Mr. Peiris made a special statement in the parliament and said that they will become independent."
      ],
